channel.title: How do i login to other peoples servers?
channel.description: when i tried to use the ip to login to someones server, it just came up with unexpected response from server, please use another world. i went to the server status page and i use a server from my port (53594) typed in the ip, but it said that. What should i do? do i need to connect up with hamachi somehow?[br][size=1]Posted on: May 04, 2007, 02:53:10 AM[/size][hr]omfg its been like 2 hours... anyone..
